# Project Rules

## Project Name
Dream Avenue

## Project Description
Dream Avenue - A wedding planning and management platform

## Code Style Guidelines
- Use TypeScript for all components
- Follow React best practices
- Use functional components with hooks
- Maintain consistent naming conventions
- Keep components modular and reusable

## Component Structure
- Place UI components in `src/components/ui/`
- Place section components in `src/components/sections/`
- Each section should have its own directory

## Naming Conventions
- Use PascalCase for component files and names
- Use camelCase for variables and functions
- Use descriptive names that convey purpose

## Development Guidelines
- Ensure responsive design for all components
- Optimize for performance
- Follow accessibility best practices
- Write clean, maintainable code

